There are three types of APIs:=C2=A0
Internal APIs: Used to do complex things more simply within a company.=C2=
=A0
Public APIs: Typically used to open up datasets so others can build on top =
of them.=C2=A0
Vendor APIs: Give customers the full superpowers of an entire company in a =
few lines of code.
